# coul/esp correctness test (Step 4: pair_coul_esp_omp verification)
# PairCoulEsp : public Pair (KSPACE package). Pure Coulombic pair style used with
# kspace_style esp (polynomial-spreading fast-Ewald). Force/energy use either a
# direct Horner-polynomial evaluation (force_poly_coeff/energy_poly_coeff, sourced
# from the ESP kspace object) for rsq <= tabinnersq, or the same A1-A5-free
